37:01.360 --> 37:05.809
I said we'd have a family meeting,
take a vote.

37:13.640 --> 37:15.085
Well, why not? Hmm?

37:16.200 --> 37:18.885
We've no truck with Fenians
or communists.

37:24.480 --> 37:25.811
