Have you not seen the streets?

45:57.600 --> 46:00.126
They've sent a fucking army
to find these things.

46:00.240 --> 46:01.526
That's right.

46:01.800 --> 46:03.040
They've shown their hand.

46:03.640 --> 46:04.687
Their hand?

46:04.760 --> 46:07.331
If they want them back this bad,
they'll have to pay.

46:07.600 --> 46:09.170
That's the way of the world.

46:09.960 --> 46:12.042
Fortune drops something
valuable into your lap,

46:12.120 --> 46:14.122
you don't just dump it
on the bank of the cut.

46:17.320 --> 46:18.890
You're blood, Tommy.

46:20.160 --> 46:22.208
I've always looked out for you
like a dad.

46:25.240 --> 46:27.766
You're going to bring
only hell down on your head.

46:29.800 --> 46:31.564
This copper takes no prisoners.

46:32.960 --> 46:34.405
I'm told he didn't serve.

46:36.080 --> 46:37.570
Reserved occupation.

46:41.000 --> 46:43.287
Is it another war
you're looking for, Tommy?

46:44.720 --> 46:46.085
The tobacco wharf.

46:47.880 --> 46:49.848
By order of the Peaky Blinders.

47:21.480 --> 47:22.845
Are you in position?

47:26.080 --> 47:27.206
I am, sir.

47:29.000 --> 47:30.240
First impressions?

47:31.560 --> 47:33.961
I'm quite shocked
at how these people live.

47:37.200 --> 47:39.441
Have you found anything out
that might help me?

47:39.640 --> 47:41.847
I interrogated the head
of the Peaky Blinders.

47:42.800 --> 47:43.926
He didn't know anything.

47:44.520 --> 47:45.521
A brute.

47:45.920 --> 47:49.288
It strikes me that it isn't Arthur
who heads the Shelby family.

47:49.720 --> 47:51.404
It's the younger one.

47:51.600 --> 47:52.761
Thomas.

47:55.040 --> 47:57.486
They say he won two medals
for gallantry in the war.

47:58.640 --> 48:00.244
You sound fascinated.

48:03.040 --> 48:05.850
However, my opinion has not changed.

48:07.040 --> 48:08.804
The bookmaker gangs have other business

48:08.880 --> 48:11.326
and the communists
are too weak to have planned this.

48:13.600 --> 48:15.841
I believe the guns
were taken by the IRA.

48:18.520 --> 48:22.844
You must not let your personal history
cloud yourjudgement.

48:27.640 --> 48:28.641
What history?

48:31.000 --> 48:35.005
